&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Reports to:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Delivery Leader (HQ-direct portfolios) or Hub Leader (hub-embedded portfolios)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Direct reports: &lt;/span&gt;1–6 Deltas / FDEs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Location: &lt;strong&gt;Hybrid: Charleston, South Carolina or Quantico, Virginia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
