&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;This is a leadership role with technical depth. You won’t be writing pipelines all day, but you need enough hands-on Foundry fluency to identify a bad design, pair with a Delta on a stuck problem, and credibly own the architecture conversation with the customer.&lt;/p&gt;
