&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Embed with the customer&lt;/strong&gt;, participate in user research and &lt;strong&gt;quickly prototype solutions&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and execute innovative software solutions &lt;strong&gt;tailored to customer missions&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build &amp;amp; lead delivery&lt;/strong&gt; of secure, scalable code from concept to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide &lt;strong&gt;leadership&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;mentorship &lt;/strong&gt;to grow team capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct &lt;strong&gt;technical solution research&lt;/strong&gt; and track product trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with your Echo to &lt;strong&gt;translate product vision into technical reality&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure &lt;strong&gt;code quality, security, and maintainability&lt;/strong&gt; through reviews and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
